{"id": "1405140034646048849", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 0, "author_id": "504954153865576448", "author_name": "murphy.p", "author_bot": false, "content": "(グローバル版/Steam版で先行プレイしているけど、ゲーム性を胸を張って紹介できるほどの知識はないからオレンジロールにしてる人多そう)(自己紹介)", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T10:44:50.499000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405171548276523029", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 0, "author_id": "1396445222107484160", "author_name": "demondontcry1275", "author_bot": false, "content": "日本でリリースされるのが初めての人なんですがこのゲームってグローバル版ではどんな評価なんですか？", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T12:50:03.934000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-13T12:56:31.315000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405183726241054770", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 0, "author_id": "414694381870907395", "author_name": "miyakei", "author_bot": false, "content": "中小企業のゲームで成功したケースとして評価は高いですよ、chat GPTを使用して翻訳を行った事でローカライズで殆どが失敗する中で唯一生き残ってる珍しい例。", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T13:38:27.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405184988827091067", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 0, "author_id": "414694381870907395", "author_name": "miyakei", "author_bot": false, "content": "ゲームの内容としての評価はシナリオが評価されてる(合う人には評価高い)、ゲームシステムは良くあるタイプ(黒潮之上や重反未来系)で動作は結構重め。STEAM版なら違和感無い", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T13:43:28.411000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405310779166560428", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 0, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "大陸版で半年くらいやってます。一応現行キャラは全部持ってて、エンドコンテンツをつま先だけやってる感じです", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T22:03:19.165000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "fufufu", "emoji_id": "1390952956546908170", "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405310841326141482", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 19, "author_id": "1396445222107484160", "author_name": "demondontcry1275", "author_bot": false, "content": "かなり好評のゲームなんですね✨\n動作が重めってところがちょっと気になりますけどその分結構こだわってるってことでしょうか....かなり楽しみになりました。情報ありがとうございます！😊", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T22:03:33.985000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["414694381870907395"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1405184988827091067", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1405311095245111326", "channel_id": "1377478664609857647", "type": 19, "author_id": "493650914025144321", "author_name": "nin0876", "author_bot": false, "content": "FGOを研究してますね。シナリオ進めるとキャラが欲しくなります", "timestamp": "2025-08-13T22:04:34.524000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["414694381870907395"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1405184988827091067", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
